                     <interp inst="t18230409-126-person1135" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. I went to the prosecutor's house, and found a handkerchief in a bundle.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner. I never saw the sovereigns.</p>
               <p>GUILTY. Aged 34.</p>
